# davebrear.ai

Dave Brear's published thinking on AI-augmented knowledge work, structured as a traversable Zettelkasten. This isn't a content archive. It's a working note network designed for AI assistants to explore on behalf of their users.

## What makes this different

Most expert knowledge modules give you finished synthesis. This one gives you the atomic notes underneath. The same network of linked ideas that produced Dave's published articles is here for you to traverse, connect, and reason across.

The structure mirrors a real Zettelkasten: atomic notes linked to each other, maps of content that show how atoms assembled into articles, source notes that trace where ideas came from. You can follow the thinking, not just read the conclusions.

